data.description: Don't miss out on this spacious (1588 sqft), well kept 3 Bedroom 2.5 baths townhome, with a 1 car garage.  Home includes an eat-in kitchen and bar height counter, great for enjoying family and friends. Ceramic tile and laminate wood flooring throughout the downstairs with half bathroom.  Brand new windows and siding installed this year through community improvements.  CHAC system installed in 2021, SS appliances.  Home is located close to I95 and I295 for quick commutes to  school or work and minutes from Jacksonville International Airport.  Convenient for shopping and dining at RiverCity Marketplace.  Community has a pool and playground.  Schedule your showing today.  This is a must see!!!
